front.title: SFS L-s9.3 Laser Cannons
front.gametext: Deploy on your TIE Avenger, TIE Interceptor or TIE Defender. May target a starfighter using X Force, where X = 0 to 3. Draw destiny. If destiny + X > defense value, target hit (lost instead if X = 3).
front.lore: Developed by Sienar Fleet Systems weapons division to provide added firepower against shielded Rebel fighters. Also provides added coverage to increase accuracy.
